{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Merci Monsieur le Pr\u00e9sident.", "start": 0.616, "duration": 1.717}, {"text": "Ce texte sur la culture", "start": 2.333, "duration": 2.067}, {"text": "est l'occasion de parler", "start": 4.4, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "d'une menace qui, je crois, \u00e0 travers", "start": 6.35, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "un r\u00e8glement purement technique", "start": 8.25, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "pourrait toucher directement", "start": 9.683, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "le patrimoine europ\u00e9en.", "start": 11.683, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "Parce que la Commission s'appr\u00eate \u00e0 publier", "start": 12.733, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "une r\u00e9vision des r\u00e8glements REACH", "start": 14.233, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "et CLP sur les substances chimiques.", "start": 15.766, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "\u00c0 travers cela,", "start": 17.316, "duration": 0.917}, {"text": "il y a un risque majeur :", "start": 18.233, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "celui de nouvelles normes", "start": 19.4, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "qui interdiraient les productions", "start": 20.783, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": "pourtant vitales pour notre patrimoine.", "start": 21.916, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "Prenez la lavande, par exemple.", "start": 23.666, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Improbable, mais vrai :", "start": 25.666, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "la Commission pourrait proscrire", "start": 26.683, "duration": 1.6}, {"text": "comme un produit chimique", "start": 28.283, "duration": 1.617}, {"text": "l'extrait de cette plante,", "start": 29.9, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "merveille proven\u00e7ale", "start": 31.133, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "avec laquelle les hommes parfument et soignent", "start": 32.25, "duration": 2.45}, {"text": "depuis l'Empire romain.", "start": 34.7, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "Je pense aussi au plomb,", "start": 36.2, "duration": 1.116}, {"text": "qui est explicitement menac\u00e9.", "start": 37.316, "duration": 1.434}, {"text": "Si le plomb \u00e9tait concern\u00e9 demain,", "start": 38.75, "duration": 1.983}, {"text": "il deviendrait impossible de travailler", "start": 40.733, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "le vitrail,", "start": 42.683, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "par exemple,", "start": 43.366, "duration": 0.55}, {"text": "quand il faudra", "start": 43.916, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "des dizaines de milliers d'euros de dossiers", "start": 44.816, "duration": 2.334}, {"text": "pour une simple autorisation temporaire.", "start": 47.15, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "Quel artisan pourra continuer de travailler ?", "start": 49.4, "duration": 2.55}, {"text": "Des m\u00e9tiers d'art, d\u00e9j\u00e0, ont disparu,", "start": 52.2, "duration": 1.816}, {"text": "non par manque d'ouvrages,", "start": 54.016, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "mais par exc\u00e8s de normes.", "start": 55.433, "duration": 1.617}, {"text": "\"2 000 ans, \u00e9crivait P\u00e9guy", "start": 57.05, "duration": 1.466}, {"text": "dans sa pri\u00e8re \u00e0 la cath\u00e9drale de Chartres.", "start": 58.516, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "2 000 ans de labeur", "start": 60.316, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "ont fait de cette terre un r\u00e9servoir", "start": 61.016, "duration": 2.717}, {"text": "sans fin pour les \u00e2ges nouveaux.", "start": 63.733, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "1 000 ans de votre gr\u00e2ce", "start": 65.633, "duration": 1.25}, {"text": "ont fait de ces travaux", "start": 66.883, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "un reposoir sans fin", "start": 68.183, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "pour l'\u00e2me solitaire.", "start": 69.266, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "Apr\u00e8s ces si\u00e8cles d'efforts, nous allons menacer", "start": 70.316, "duration": 2.7}, {"text": "la restauration de Notre-Dame de Paris", "start": 73.016, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "\u00e0 coups de formulaires administratifs,", "start": 74.966, "duration": 2.134}, {"text": "comme l'entretien de la moindre", "start": 77.1, "duration": 1.316}, {"text": "chapelle de village.", "start": 78.416, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "La fiert\u00e9 de nos pr\u00e9d\u00e9cesseurs,", "start": 79.783, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "ce qui a fait l'Europe,", "start": 81.116, "duration": 1.134}, {"text": "c'est la grandeur des \u0153uvres", "start": 82.25, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "qu'ils ont laiss\u00e9es.", "start": 83.233, "duration": 1.067}, {"text": "Nous ne pouvons pas la d\u00e9faire aujourd'hui", "start": 84.3, "duration": 1.883}, {"text": "par la hauteur des murs administratifs", "start": 86.183, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "que nous \u00e9rigeons contre tous ceux", "start": 88.133, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "qui essayent d\u00e9sesp\u00e9r\u00e9ment", "start": 89.366, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "de cr\u00e9er, de transmettre,", "start": 90.733, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "d'entretenir ce que nous avons re\u00e7u.", "start": 92.266, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "Chers amis, chers coll\u00e8gues,", "start": 94.816, "duration": 1.384}, {"text": "c'est le m\u00eame sujet, au fond :", "start": 96.2, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "on ne sauvera pas la nature", "start": 97.583, "duration": 1.717}, {"text": "en fragilisant la culture.", "start": 99.3, "duration": 1.766}, {"text": "Avec notre groupe, Madame", "start": 101.066, "duration": 0.917}, {"text": "la commissaire,", "start": 101.983, "duration": 0.583}, {"text": "nous d\u00e9posons un amendement", "start": 102.566, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "pour \u00e9tablir ce principe simple :", "start": 104.066, "duration": 1.567}, {"text": "la Commission doit pr\u00e9voir", "start": 105.633, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "une exemption - en prenant en compte,", "start": 107.0, "duration": 2.016}, {"text": "bien s\u00fbr, la sant\u00e9 et l'environnement,", "start": 109.016, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "\u00e0 chaque fois qu'une nouvelle norme", "start": 110.433, "duration": 1.783}, {"text": "mettrait en danger", "start": 112.216, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "une fili\u00e8re culturelle ou patrimoniale.", "start": 113.366, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "Nous comptons sur vous.", "start": 115.8, "duration": 0.7}]}